qas.question: In what did the bagpipe fill an important role?
What instrument gained prominence in the 19th and 20th century?
Vihuelas and hurdy-gurdies are currently associated with what type of music?

context: Many instruments today associated with <a2_0>popular<a2_0/> music filled important roles in <a0_0>early classical music,<a0_0/> such as bagpipes, vihuelas, hurdy-gurdies, and some woodwind instruments.
